VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \beval\s*\(|assert\s*\(\s*\$|create_function\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:validate|allowlist|trusted|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dangerous dynamic code execution primitives in PHP code paths.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Codeigniter Dangerous Dynamic Eval/Template Execution.
